dc_description_s: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development. Division of Planning and Development. Atlas Sheet 32 (1955) New Jersey Geological Survey. Alternate title: [New Jersey.] Topographic series. Sheet 32. Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings in feet at low tide. Title is not given. Region covered: southern Burlington County. Original survey made under direction of C. C. Vermuele, Topographer in 1880-3, 1955 revision by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dc_publisher_s: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1955.
